    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/546a0e6d49ee97d4662d63e383c9fe65.poster.avif?t=1767800395\" aria-label=\"The player enters &amp;quot;The Jungle Expedition&amp;quot; encounter\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/546a0e6d49ee97d4662d63e383c9fe65.webm?t=1767800395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/546a0e6d49ee97d4662d63e383c9fe65.mp4?t=1767800395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/7b66040d4645486f6c1509416003293a.avif?t=1767800395\" alt=\"A New Kind of Strategy Game\" width=800 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到英雄构筑策略游戏《The Bazaar》</strong>！加入充满活力、不断变化的银河大巴扎，收集各类奇妙工具和武器，让它们在你手中变成战略阵容，然后释放战力，与怪奇生物和敌对玩家一较高下！数百个完全配音的独特奇遇，呼唤着渴望淘金的《The Bazaar》冒险者前来一探究竟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为Meta大神，还是个性出装制胜，都由你自己选择。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/6307ded6567ebf36049cdb98819d684f.poster.avif?t=1767800395\" aria-label=\"The Hero Select screen of The Bazaar\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/6307ded6567ebf36049cdb98819d684f.webm?t=1767800395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/6307ded6567ebf36049cdb98819d684f.mp4?t=1767800395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/8e6c1d7e1caed452529d7a0036668bfe.avif?t=1767800395\" alt=\"Build Your Hero, Guard Your Prestige\" width=800 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>英雄阵容持续拓展</strong>，每一位都有自己独一无二的打法和风格。选择你最喜欢的英雄，入手超过100种独特物品，享受不断充实和发展的精彩内容。装备武器、技能、工具、药水、恐龙以及更多，构筑究极战略，在战场上掀起毁灭的风暴，摧枯拉朽击败敌人！数百种物品和组合等你发现，每一局都是等待被解开的独特谜题。选择前要三思哦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/0197baa3d3a688d4907f6c6be0331782.poster.avif?t=1767800395\" aria-label=\"Combat showing The Boulder item crushing the opponent\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/0197baa3d3a688d4907f6c6be0331782.webm?t=1767800395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/0197baa3d3a688d4907f6c6be0331782.mp4?t=1767800395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>按照你自己的节奏规划冒险。</strong>在旅途中，你会遇到其他真实玩家，体验战略规划和创造力碰撞出的独特奇遇，又没有即时操作的压力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/97d93bb696836c86a6312edd2288ff4a.poster.avif?t=1767800395\" aria-label=\"Combat in The Bazaar showcasing the &amp;quot;Stopwatch&amp;quot; effect, freezing both players&#039; boards.\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/97d93bb696836c86a6312edd2288ff4a.webm?t=1767800395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/97d93bb696836c86a6312edd2288ff4a.mp4?t=1767800395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/ff55b39ba889e430f171225140d744f8.avif?t=1767800395\" alt=\"Infinite Possibilities\" width=800 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创意和冒险精神是《The Bazaar》胜利的窍门。你可以围绕一件强大物品构建整套手牌，一拳克敌制胜，也可以调配巧妙的组合，在连锁反应中享受凯旋的美妙滋味。没有标准答案，没有单调反复的刷刷刷，能随机变通、适应并超越困境的，才是真正的王者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/7199503b63404058e04a8407705e7afa.poster.avif?t=1767800395\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/7199503b63404058e04a8407705e7afa.webm?t=1767800395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/7199503b63404058e04a8407705e7afa.mp4?t=1767800395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1617400/extras/6c33334aba44ea7ab8e9751e08759d1b.avif?t=1767800395\" alt=\"Uncover the Mysteries of The Bazaar\" width=800 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>大巴扎里不只有战斗！</strong>每位英雄都有自己独特的旅程，而你也会在冒险中遇到各种各样令人难忘的全配音角色，从热情友善的商人，到革命家机器人，再到动机成谜的强大存在，让你沉浸在富有氛围感的鲜活世界中无法自拔。魔法、机器和上古秘密在《The Bazaar》亦真亦幻的岔路口交汇。走进这个充满高科技奇幻色彩的世界，踏上一次又一次的冒险，逐渐揭开其中蕴藏的深厚世界观。</p>",
